scrabble challenge pseudo code 

understanding of challenge : 

input - input a string value ( word)
each letter in the english alphabet has a value preassigned to it already

process - run the value through functions, loops and conditionals to them give me my output 
charcters and null should return 0


output - a numeric value based on the word.

step 1 
create my array with my letter scores in a let variable. 
add guard feature so function will work with a non string null value. 


step 2 
create a loop that will fetch the letter values from the array. 
sum the values of your scrabbleword or if not a valid input return 0

step 3 
return sum 

step 4 
console.log ( scrabble (scrabbledWord))

